rows.name:
My husband often goes to
the large public bath in
the center of the city.

rows.label: qst102907_msg002
rows.name:
He says he was in charge of some
of the carvings in the bathhouse.

rows.label: qst102907_msg101
rows.name:
I'm sure my husband is at the
large public bath in the city
center today as well.
